items.title: Length extension attack - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Length extension attack - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
Note that since HMAC doesn't use the construction H(key ∥ message), HMAC 
hashes using susceptible algorithms are not prone to length extension attacks.
